<h3>Day-1</h3>
# Dockerized Wedding Website

## 📌 Project Overview
This mini project demonstrates how to containerize a static website using Docker and deploy it with Nginx.

## 🚀 What I Did
- Created a custom `Dockerfile`
- Used the official **Nginx** image as the base image
- Copied the website files into the Nginx web root
- Built a Docker image
- Ran a Docker container exposing **port 80**
- Verified the website was accessible through the container

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Docker
- Nginx
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Linux
- Servers
- AWS

