## 🐳 Docker Commands

### Build the Docker Image
```bash
docker build -t wedding-main .
```

### Run the Container
```bash
docker run -d -p 80:80 --name wedding-container wedding-main
```

### Verify Running Containers
```bash
docker ps
```

